WEBVTT

00:04:28.221 --> 00:04:31.146
Si perdies, mories.

00:04:31.146 --> 00:04:33.490
Com la va vèncer Hipòmenes?

00:04:33.490 --> 00:04:35.416
Tenia unes pometes daurades meravelloses,

00:04:35.416 --> 00:04:38.034
i ella corria davant i ell feia rodar
una pometa daurada.

